00782       private bool CheckStack(TreeNode node, Boolean pop)
00783       {
00784          if ((node.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.SLIST || node.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.SCOPEEXPR) &&
00785             (node.ChildIndex != node.Parent.ChildCount - 1 || (node.Parent.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.WHILE && node.Parent.ChildIndex != 0) ||
00786             (node.Parent.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.METHOD && ((MethodInfo)((TreeNode)node.Parent.Parent).Entry.ReflectionObject).ReturnType == typeof(void)) ||
00787             node.Parent.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.CONSTRUCTOR || node.Parent.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.SCONSTRUCTOR) &&
00788             node.ReturnType != typeof(void))
00789          {
00790             if (pop) ig.Emit(OpCodes.Pop);
00791             return false;
00792          }
00793          else if (node.Parent.Type == VnvdGenerator.IF && node.ChildIndex != 0 && node.ReturnType != typeof(void) && ((TreeNode)node.Parent).ReturnType == typeof(void))
00794          {
00795             if (pop) ig.Emit(OpCodes.Pop);
00796             return false;
00797          }
00798          return true;
00799       }

00808       public override void CastExpression(TreeNode node, Qualifier qual)
00809       {
00810          Type dest = (Type)node.Entry.ReflectionObject;
00811          Type src = ((TreeNode)node.GetChild(1)).ReturnType;
00812          if (src is UserType)
00813             src = (Type)((UserType)src).Entry.ReflectionObject;
00814 
00815          if (src.IsValueType && dest == typeof(object))
00816          {
00817             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Box, src);
00818          }
00819          else if (src == typeof(object) && dest.IsValueType)
00820          {
00821             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Unbox, dest);
00822             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Ldobj, dest);
00823          }
00824          else if (src.IsPrimitive && dest.IsPrimitive)
00825          {
00826             if (dest == typeof(int) || dest == typeof(char))
00827                ig.Emit(OpCodes.Conv_I4);
00828             else if (dest == typeof(byte))
00829                ig.Emit(OpCodes.Conv_I1);
00830             else if (dest == typeof(double))
00831                ig.Emit(OpCodes.Conv_R8);
00832          }
00833          else
00834          {
00835             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Castclass, dest);
00836          }
00837       }

00900       public override void AccessArray(TreeNode node)
00901       {
00902          if (node.Parent.Type != VnvdGenerator.BECOMES || node.ChildIndex == node.Parent.ChildCount - 1)
00903          {
00904             if (node.EntryType == EntryType.Constant)
00905             {
00906                Type t = ((UserLocal)node.Entry.ReflectionObject).LocalType.GetElementType();
00907                if (t.Equals(typeof(Int32)))
00908                {
00909                   this.LiteralNumber(node);
00910                }
00911                else if (t.Equals(typeof(Double)))
00912                {
00913                   this.LiteralFloat(node);
00914                }
00915                else if (t.Equals(typeof(String)))
00916                {
00917                   this.LiteralString(node);
00918                }
00919                else if (t.Equals(typeof(Char)))
00920                {
00921                   this.LiteralCharacter(node);
00922                }
00923                else if (t.Equals(typeof(Boolean)))
00924                {
00925                   this.LiteralBoolean(node);
00926                }
00927             }
00928             else
00929             {
00930                ig.Emit(OpCodes.Ldelem, GetRuntimeType(node.ReturnType));
00931             }
00932          }
00933       }

00964       public override void BeginFor(TreeNode node, TreeNode node2, Qualifier qual, string p)
00965       {
00966          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Callvirt, typeof(IEnumerable).GetMethod("GetEnumerator"));
00967 
00968          Label forEnd = ig.DefineLabel();
00969          forEndLabels.Push(forEnd);
00970 
00971          Label forLabel = ig.DefineLabel();
00972          forStartLabels.Push(forLabel);
00973          ig.MarkLabel(forLabel);
00974          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Dup);
00975          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Callvirt, typeof(IEnumerator).GetMethod("MoveNext"));
00976          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Brfalse, forEnd);
00977          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Dup);
00978          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Callvirt, typeof(IEnumerator).GetMethod("get_Current"));
00979          LocalBuilder l = (LocalBuilder)node2.Entry.ReflectionObject;
00980          if (l.LocalType.IsValueType)
00981          {
00982             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Unbox, l.LocalType);
00983             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Ldobj, l.LocalType);
00984          }
00985          else
00986             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Castclass, l.LocalType);
00987 
00988          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Stloc, l);
00989       }

01010             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(Console).GetMethod("ReadKey", Type.EmptyTypes));
01011

01013             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Ldloca, lb2);
01014 
01015             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(ConsoleKeyInfo).GetMethod("get_KeyChar"));
01016          }
01017          else if (lb.LocalType == typeof(int))
01018          {
01019             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(Console).GetMethod("ReadLine"));
01020             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(Int32).GetMethod("Parse", new Type[] { typeof(string) }));

01022          else if (lb.LocalType == typeof(bool))
01023          {
01024             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(Console).GetMethod("ReadLine"));

01026          }
01027          else
01028          {
01029             ig.Emit(OpCodes.Call, typeof(Console).GetMethod("ReadLine"));
01030          }
01031 
01032          //if (lb.LocalType == typeof(object) && child.ReturnType.IsValueType)
01033          //    ig.Emit(OpCodes.Box, child.ReturnType);
01034 
01035          ig.Emit(OpCodes.Stloc, lb);
